org.sbml.jsbml

Class FunctionDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sbml.jsbml.AbstractTreeNode
      • org.sbml.jsbml.AbstractSBase
        • org.sbml.jsbml.AbstractMathContainer
          • org.sbml.jsbml.FunctionDefinition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode, CallableSBase, MathContainer, NamedSBase, NamedSBaseWithDerivedUnit, SBase, SBaseWithDerivedUnit, UniqueNamedSBase, TreeNodeWithChangeSupport

    public class FunctionDefinition
extends AbstractMathContainer
implements CallableSBase, UniqueNamedSBase
    Represents the functionDefinition XML element of a SBML file. Since FunctionDefinitions were introduced to SBML in Level 2, this class must not be used for models in Level 1.
    Since:
    0.8
    Version:
    $Rev: 1447 $
    Author:
    Andreas Dräger, Marine Dumousseau
